Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: YAML parsing errors

Solution: Validate YAML syntax using yamllint or online validators
Check for proper indentation (use spaces, not tabs)
Issue: Import errors for custom modules

Solution: Ensure you're in the correct directory and virtual environment is activated
Add sys.path.append() if needed for module discovery
Issue: Matplotlib display issues

Solution: Use plt.savefig() instead of plt.show() in headless environments
Install python3-tk if GUI display is needed
Issue: Division by zero in score calculations

Solution: Add validation to check for empty response lists
Implement default values for missing data
